Available Commands
Command	Description
npm install	Install dependencies
npm start	Start the API server
npm run dev	Start with Nodemon (auto-restart)
mongod --dbpath /data/db	Start MongoDB locally
node server.js	Run the API manually
Dependencies Used ğŸ“¦
Package	Purpose
express	Web framework for Node.js
mongoose	MongoDB ODM for managing database
dotenv	Loads environment variables from .env
nodemon (dev)	Restarts server on file changes
API Endpoints
POST /api/quiz/create â†’ Create a quiz

GET /api/quiz/ â†’ Get all quizzes

POST /api/quiz/play â†’ Play a quiz & get score

Testing the API with Postman
Open Postman and create requests:

POST /api/quiz/create â†’ Create a quiz

GET /api/quiz/ â†’ Retrieve quizzes

POST /api/quiz/play â†’ Submit answers

